# Library Management System

Welcome to the Library Management System repository! This project is a library management system implemented in Kotlin. It allows you to  search, and manage books in a library.

## Features

- Search for books by their ID, title, or author name.
- Remove books from the library.
- Track the books that are borrowed
- Display all books in the library.

## Technologies Used

- Kotlin
- IntelliJ IDEA

## How to Use

1. Clone this repository to your local machine.
2. Open the project in IntelliJ IDEA.
3. Build and run the project.

## Usage

Here's an example of how you can add multiple books to the library:

https://youtu.be/C0VfFmofFCI

